Letty Alonzo (born 1932) is a Filipina actress from LVN Pictures who was typecast as a Villain. She made only a few movies.

== Personal life ==
She was married to another famous LVN star, the late Mario Montenegro. Her granddaughter Valeen Montenegro is an up-and-coming young actress.

== Filmography ==
1951 - Bohemyo
1953 - Senorito
1953 - 3 Labuyo
1953 - Batanguena

